ia scheduled for March and April, in support of his most recently released album of the same name.</p><h2> Waterbomb Manila </h2><figure id="attachment_3831673" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3831673" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3831673" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/waterbomb-manila-february-2025-line-up.jpg" alt="waterbomb manila february 2025 line-up" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/waterbomb-manila-february-2025-line-up.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/waterbomb-manila-february-2025-line-up-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/waterbomb-manila-february-2025-line-up-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/waterbomb-manila-february-2025-line-up-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/waterbomb-manila-february-2025-line-up-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/waterbomb-manila-february-2025-line-up-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3831673" class="wp-caption-text"> LR: Epik High&#39;s Mithra Jin, Kwon Eunbi, EXO&#39;s Chanyeol. Credit: Timothy Norris, The Chosunilbo JNS, Han Myung-gu/Getty Images</figcaption></figure><p> <strong>Saturday, February 22 – Day 1<br /></strong> Epik High<br />动态二人组<br />Kim Jong-kook<br /> EXO&#39;s Chanyeol<br /> Baekho<br /> MAMAMOO&#39;s Hwasa<br />双<br />Kwon Eunbi<br /> Lee Chaeyeon<br /> STAYC<br /> Raiden<br /> ZB &amp; AITON<br /> DJ Roots<br /> JEB<br /> IMLAY<br /> Apro<br /> Thea Astley</p><p> <strong>Sunday, February 23 – Day 2</strong><br />杰西<br />桑米<br />Hyolyn<br />灰色的<br />GOT7&#39;s BamBam<br /> Skull &amp; HaHa<br /> OH MY GIRL<br /> Kang Daniel<br /> Reddy<br /> VIVIZ<br /> Yang Se-chan<br /> Sulreggae<br /> U-Kwon<br /> InsideCore<br /> Aster &amp; Neo<br 