ascal">佩德罗·帕斯卡（Pedro Pascal）</a>和贝拉·拉姆西（Bella Ramsey）分别扮演 - 以及凯特琳·德弗（Kaitlyn Dever）的艾比·安德森（Abby Anderson），扬·马齐诺（Abby Anderson），扬·马齐诺（Abby Anderson），扬·马齐诺（Abby Anderson），伊莎贝拉·梅塞贝拉（Isabela Merced）的迪纳（Dina）和丹尼·拉米雷斯（Danny Ramirez）的曼尼（Manny）。 Ariela Barer，Tati Gabrielle，Spencer Lord，Jeffrey Wright和Catherine O&#39;Hara还将以新演员为特色。</p><p> While there are currently only two <a href="https://www.nme.com/games/the-last-of-us"><em>The Last Of Us</em></a> games to pull from currently, HBO&#39;s drama chief Francesca Orci earlier this month <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/gaming-news/the-last-of-us-will-probably-run-for-four-seasons-3838017">suggested that the show could run for four seasons</a> : “We don&#39;t have a complete or final plan, but I think it&#39;s looking like four seasons.我不想确认这一点，但是这个季节看起来像是在此之后的两个季节，我们完成了。”</p><p> Her comment echoes that of showrunner Craig Mazin, <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/tv/hbo-the-last-of-us-could-last-four-seasons-3484244">who in August 2023 revealed they were eyeing a four-season run</a> : “It can end up being three or five.但是四个似乎是一个不错的数字。由于我们讲的故事，有些季节将需要更少的情节，有些则需要更多。最好的消息是观众想要更多，但我们不会更愿意让他们更加快乐。” </p><figure id="attachment_3568111" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3568111" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3568111" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Pedro-Pascal-The-Last-Of-Us.jpg" alt="我们最后一个" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Pedro-Pascal-The-Last-Of-Us.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Pedro-Pascal-The-Last-Of-Us-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Pedro-Pascal-The-Last-Of-Us-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Pedro-Pascal-The-Last-Of-Us-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Pedro-Pascal-The-Last-Of-Us-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Pedro-Pascal-The-Last-Of-Us-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3568111" class="wp-caption-text">佩德罗·帕斯卡（Pedro Pascal）和贝拉·拉姆西（Bella Ramsey</figcaption></figure><p> Game creator Neil Druckmann <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/gaming-news/naughty-dog-might-never-make-the-last-of-us-part-3-3387414">took a similar stance with <em>The Last Of Us Part 3</em></a> . “仅仅因为某些事情是成功的，人们都认为存在所有这些压力，我们必须制作续集。事实并非如此。”他说。但是，有关游戏制作的新纪录片表明，第三款游戏有一个“概念”。 <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/gaming-news/naughty-dog-teases-one-more-chapter-with-the-last-of-us-part-3-3582616">“It does feel like there&#39;s probably one more chapter to this story</a> .”</p><p> Mazin also recently explained how <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/gaming-news/the-last-of-us-season-two-differences-from-game-3835035">the second season of <em>The Last Of Us</em> will differ from the games</a> . “暂时没有太多的暴力行动。这更多是关于戏剧的。我并不是说这里没有行动。同样，这是不同的优先事项以及您如何处理它。”</p><p> The post <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/tv/the-last-of-us-heres-when-season-two-is-coming-out-3839629">&#39;The Last Of Us&#39;: here&#39;s when season two is coming out</a> appeared first on <a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a> .</p> ;
