at the Queen Sirikit Convention Center. Later on, she will play two shows in Tokyo, on March 17 and 18, at the Saitama Super Arena.</p><p> Venues and ticketing information have yet to be announced. However, Blissoo&#39;s initial announcement stated that that details will be done through Jisoo&#39;s newly launched app. Keep tabs on this page for the latest updates.</p><h2> The dates for Jisoo&#39;s 2025 &#39;Lights, Love, Action!&#39; tour are:</h2><p> <strong>2025年3月<br />14: Manila, the Philippines, Smart Araneta Coliseum<br /></strong> <strong>15: Bangkok, Thailand, Queen Sirikit Convention Center</strong><br /> <strong>17: Tokyo, Japan, Saitama Super Arena</strong><br /> <strong>18: Tokyo, Japan, Saitama Super Arena<br /></strong></p><p> <strong>TBA</strong><br />中国澳门<br />台湾台北<br />香港，中国<br />河内，越南</p><blockquote class="twitter-tweet" data-width="550" data-dnt="true"><p lang="th" dir="ltr"><img src="https://s.w.org/images/core/emoji/15.0.3/72x72/1f493.png" alt="💓" class="wp-smiley" style="height: 1em; max-height: 1em;" /><img src="https://s.w.org/images/core/emoji/15.0.3/72x72/1f493.png" alt="💓" class="wp-smiley" style="height: 1em; max-height: 1em;" /> ตึก ตึก ตึก <img src="https://s.w.org/images/core/emoji/15.0.3/72x72/1f493.png" alt="💓" class="wp-smiley" style="height: 1em; max-height: 1em;" /><img src="https://s.w.org/images/core/emoji/15.0.3/72x72/1f493.png" alt="💓" class="wp-smiley" style="height: 1em; max-height: 1em;" /> อัตราการเต้นของหัวใจเต้นแรงขนาดนี้เพราะ…<br /> 2025 JISOO ASIA TOUR : &quot;LIGHTS, LOVE, ACTION!&quot; IN BANGKOK มาแล้ววววววว <img src="https://s.w.org/images/core/emoji/15.0.3/72x72/2764-fe0f-200d-1f525.png" alt="❤️‍🔥" class="wp-smiley" style="height: 1em; max-height: 1em;" /></p><p> แฟนทัวร์เดี่ยวครั้งแรกของจีซู !! ที่มาพร้อมกับการปล่อยอัลบั้มเดี่ยว Amortage ที่ทำเอาแฟน ๆ… <a href="https://t.co/guVTyWhTyI">pic.twitter.com/guVTyWhTyI</a></p><p> — Simple P. Entertainment (@SimpleP_Ltd) <a href="https://twitter.com/SimpleP_Ltd/status/18