ebirth” as an artist. </p><div class="td_block_wrap tdb_single_content tdi_86 td-pb-border-top td_block_template_2 td-post-content tagdiv-type" data-td-block-uid="tdi_86" data-io-article-url="https://www.nme.com/news/music/blackpinks-jisoo-inks-partnership-with-warner-records-for-solo-career-3833444"><div class="tdb-block-inner td-fix-index"><p> In addition to her new music, Jisoo will recently starred as a lead in <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/tv/newtopia-prime-video-k-drama-teaser-cast-plot-more-blackpink-jisoo-park-jung-min-3831664">Coupang Play and Prime Video&#39;s original K-drama <em>Newtopia</em></a> , which also features <em>The 8 Show</em> actor Park Jeong-min. The apocalyptic romantic-comedy series marks the singer-actress&#39; second leading role, following 2021&#39;s <em>Snowdrop</em> .</p></div></div><p> The post <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/blackpink-jisoo-2025-lights-love-action-tour-cities-dates-tickets-more-3834354">BLACKPINK&#39;s Jisoo announces 2025 &#39;Lights, Love, Action!&#39; Asia tour</a> appeared first on <a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a> .</p> ;
